P(x,y|z) = P(y|x,z)P(x)=P(y|x,z)\sum_{z}P(x,z)=P(y|x,z)\sum_{z}P(x|z)P(z)
\sum_{z}P(x|z)P(z) \neq P(x|z)
P(x|z)
P(x)
P(x,y|z)=P(y|x,z)P(x)
 P(a,b,c,\ldots\mid u,v,w,\ldots)=\frac{P(a,b,c,\ldots, u,v,w,\ldots)}{P(u,v,w,\ldots)}. 
 P(x,y|z) =\frac{P(x,y,z)}{P(z)}\quad\&\quad P(y|x,z)=\frac{P(x,y,z)}{P(x,z)}. 
